div.h1: VGA Text Buffer: Physical 0xB8000 8025 Cell Grid

p.strong: Each cell = 2 bytes (char + attribute). Total = 4000 bytes.

g.text: Byte 0 = ASCII char | Byte 1 = attribute (bg[6:4] | fg[3:0])
volatile qualifier MANDATORY prevents compiler dead-store elimination
Cost: 1920 uint16_t reads + 1920 writes + 80 writes = 3920 MMIO ops 784s
